<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Nova NFT - Ecology Finance</title>

<style>

body{
background:#000;
color:white;
font-family:Arial;
text-align:center;
margin:0;
}

.container{
padding:20px;
max-width:420px;
margin:auto;
}

img{
width:100%;
border-radius:10px;
margin-top:20px;
}

h1{
color:#f5d77a;
margin-top:20px;
}

p{
color:#ccc;
line-height:1.5;
}

.btn{
background:linear-gradient(90deg,#ffe88a,#ffcc33);
color:black;
padding:14px;
border:none;
border-radius:10px;
font-size:18px;
width:100%;
margin-top:20px;
cursor:pointer;
}

.form{
display:none;
margin-top:20px;
}

input{
width:90%;
padding:12px;
margin:10px;
border-radius:8px;
border:none;
}

.address{
background:#111;
padding:10px;
border-radius:6px;
word-break:break-all;
margin-top:10px;
}

.success{
color:#00ff9c;
margin-top:20px;
}

.menu{
position:fixed;
bottom:0;
width:100%;
background:#111;
padding:12px;
display:flex;
justify-content:space-around;
border-top:1px solid #333;
}

.menu span{
color:white;
font-size:14px;
}

</style>

</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

<img src="ecology.png">

<h1>Ecology Finance</h1>

<p>
Investing in Ecology Finance allows you to receive withdrawals according to your wallet balance.
</p>

<p>
However, you must <b>buy Ecology Finance first</b>
</p>

<p style="color:#f5d77a">
Minimum purchase: <b>3000 USDT</b>
</p>

<button class="btn" onclick="showForm()">Invest Now</button>

<div class="form" id="form">

<p>BEP20 USDT Deposit Address</p>

<div class="address">
0xcc24EC6c4E82CA8c0D1f96C71E149a030a4663B8
</div>

<input type="text" placeholder="Enter Username">

<input type="text" placeholder="Enter UID">

<button class="btn" onclick="submitForm()">Submit</button>

</div>

<p id="msg" class="success"></p>

</div>

<div class="menu">
<span>Stake</span>
<span>Earn</span>
<span>Reserve</span>
<span>Assets</span>
<span>My</span>
</div>

<script>

function showForm(){
document.getElementById("form").style.display="block";
}

function submitForm(){
document.getElementById("msg").innerHTML=
"Successfully! Ecology Finance buy ho chuki hai. 3-4 days me update ho kar wallet me working start ho jayegi.";
}

</script>

</body>
</html>
